Colouration in life. Dorsal surface brown to light yellowish-brown; a darker brown triangular marking with a yellow central blotch between eyes; chin, chest and anterior part of belly dark brown in males or light brown with erratic dark brown blotches in females, a round white spot on each side of the chest present; posterior part of belly and ventral surface of thighs cream to dirty white; posterior part of thighs dark brown with some light blotches (
Fig. 5
).
